Pre-Game Insights: Bafana Bafana coach Hugo Broos is aware of the challenges and hopes to secure a win before the 2026 World Cup qualifiers.
Algeria's coach Vladimir Petkovic aims to start his tenure on a high with a win against South Africa.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match is the first encounter since 2015 in the Africa Cup of Nations.
Others: Bafana Bafana fans are confident after their impressive run at AFCON, while some doubt coach Broos's selections.
Key players returning to the starting lineup include Themba Zwane, Ronwen Williams, and Siyanda Xulu.
